ros en web.dev\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Colecciones de tutoriales y gu√≠as sobre web performance, accessibilidad, seguridad o PWAs entre otros en web.dev</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Este sitio de Google recoge informaci√≥n que antes estaba dispersa en distintos sitios y que ahora est√° consolidada a trav√©s de pr√°cticas gu√≠as.</p>\n<h2 id=\"herramientas\">Herramientas</h2>\n<p>Para detectar problemas de rendimiento lo mejor es hacer una auditor√≠a web. Desde el mismo navegador <a href=\"https://perf.reviews/tools/1.2-Interpretando-Lighthouse-Performance/\">se puede realizar un an√°lisis r√°pido</a>, y tambi√©n hay webs como <a href=\"https://web.dev/measure\">web.dev/measure</a> que generan un informe detallado del rendimiento de una URL en particular.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1240px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/fc364/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.07866507747319%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'224\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M199%207c0%206%200%207-2%207l-2%201h4v105l1%20105V112a6334%206334%200%2000-1-105M87%2037c-2%200-1%206%201%206%202%201%203%201%204-1l1-1c0%204%206%204%207%200%201-2%201-2%201%201%201%202%204%202%205%200%200-1%200-2-2-3-1-1-1-1%201-1v-1H95c-1%201-1%201%201%201h3l-3%201-4-1c-1-2-2-2-5-1m209%2021c-3%201-6%206-6%2010%200%2011%2015%2014%2020%204%204-8-5-18-14-14m-3%204c-4%206-1%2013%206%2015%209%201%2015-11%207-16-4-3-9-2-13%201m-129%2046l-1%207v6h30v-13l-15-1-14%201\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/277cf/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 310w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/5077d/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 620w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/e1adb/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 1240w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/92eb6/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 1860w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/d232f/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 2480w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/d75f7/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 3356w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/fa223/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 310w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/a5ed1/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 620w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/7bfa5/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 1240w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/b429f/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 1860w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/d03be/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 2480w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/fc364/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 3356w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/7bfa5/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png\"\n          alt=\"Informe de performance de perf.reviews utilizando la versi√≥n online de Lighthouse en https://web.dev/measure. Vista general y vista de informe\"\n          title=\"Informe de performance de perf.reviews utilizando la versi√≥n online de Lighthouse en https://web.dev/measure. Vista general y vista de informe\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Informe de performance de perf.reviews utilizando la versi√≥n online de Lighthouse en https://web.dev/measure. Vista general y vista de informe</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Una herramienta recomendable es <a href=\"https://webpagetest.org\">WebPageTest</a>, que tambi√©n sirve para encontrar problemas de rendimiento. Es especialmente √∫til para comparar diferentes sitios, y tambi√©n para personalizar qu√© navegador se va a usar, velocidad de red, dispositivo y ubicaci√≥n de los servidores que medir√°n el rendimiento.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1240px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/60120/webpagetest-filmstrip.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.24854530340815%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'269\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M0%20135v134h401V0H0v135m240-40v35l1-34V62h24l24-1h-49v34M41%2095v33h46V62H41v33m48%200v33h47V62H89v33m50%200v33h47V62h-47v33m51%200v33h47V62h-47v33m107-25l-4%207%202%204c2%204%204%205%207%203v-5c-4-7%200-15%206-13%201%201%201%201-1%202-2%202-2%204%202%204l2%201-2%201-1%201%202%201%201%203c-1%205%200%206%205%206%204%200%204%200%207-4l2-4-4-7-3-7h-17l-4%207m51%200l-4%206%202%205c2%203%202%204%204%203%204-1%205-2%203-5-3-5-3-11%201-12%204-2%208%200%204%201-2%202-2%204%201%204l2%202h-1l-1%201%202%201v5c-1%202%201%204%206%204%204%200%204%200%207-4l2-4-4-7-4-6-8-1h-9l-3%207M138%20172v34h49v-34l-1-29v4h-47v-8h24l24-1h-49v34m51%200v34h49l-1-29v-30h-47v-8h24l24-1h-49v34m51%200v34h48v-59h-47v-8h24l24-1h-49v34m-199%200v33h46v-66H41v33m48%200v33h47v-66H89v33m68-19c-4%204-4%2011%202%2013%202%201%203%201%204-1s2-2%203-1c2%202%205-2%205-6%200-3-4-7-8-8-2%200-3%200-6%203m51%200c-4%204-4%208%200%2012%203%203%205%203%206%200%201-2%201-2%203-1%204%203%206-7%202-11-3-4-7-4-11%200m53-2c-4%202-5%204-5%208%200%205%207%2011%208%206l4-1c6%201%206-11-1-13h-6M41%20239l1%203h26v-5l-14-1H41v3\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/277cf/webpagetest-filmstrip.webp 310w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/5077d/webpagetest-filmstrip.webp 620w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/e1adb/webpagetest-filmstrip.webp 1240w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/92eb6/webpagetest-filmstrip.webp 1860w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/4f50c/webpagetest-filmstrip.webp 2406w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/fa223/webpagetest-filmstrip.png 310w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/a5ed1/webpagetest-filmstrip.png 620w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/7bfa5/webpagetest-filmstrip.png 1240w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/b429f/webpagetest-filmstrip.png 1860w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/60120/webpagetest-filmstrip.png 2406w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/7bfa5/webpagetest-filmstrip.png\"\n          alt=\"Comparando dos sitios web con WebPagetest, vista del filmstrip\"\n          title=\"Comparando dos sitios web con WebPagetest, vista del filmstrip\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Comparando dos sitios web con WebPagetest, vista del filmstrip</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>A trav√©s de sus opciones avanzadas tambi√©n se puede <a href=\"https://andydavies.me/blog/2018/02/19/using-webpagetest-to-measure-the-impact-of-3rd-party-tags/\">comprobar el impacto de 3rd party scripts</a>, simular <a href=\"http://blog.patrickmeenan.com/2011/10/testing-for-frontend-spof.html\">single point of failures (SPOF)</a> y <a href=\"https://deanhume.com/ten-things-you-didnt-know-about-webpagetest-org/\">mucho m√°s</a>. Incluso <a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/use-webpagetest-api/\">tiene una API</a> para poder hacer todo esto desde scripts.</p>\n<p>Otras herramientas dan informes espec√≠ficos sobre optimizaci√≥n de im√°genes, como <a href=\"https://webspeedtest.cloudinary.com/\">Website Speed Test de Cloudinary</a>, o CSS con <a href=\"https://cssstats.com/\">CSS Stats</a>.</p>\n<p>Adem√°s de hacer auditor√≠as es importante medir frecuentemente cu√°l es la experiencia de usuario con herramientas RUM. Algunas de las que hemos utilizado son <a href=\"https://speedcurve.com/\">SpeedCurve</a>, <a href=\"https://www.pingdom.com/product/performance-monitoring/\">Pingdom</a>, <a href=\"https://www.akamai.com/uk/en/products/performance/mpulse-real-user-monitoring.jsp\">mPulse de Akamai</a> o desde hace poco <a href=\"https://firebase.google.com/docs/perf-mon\">Firebase</a>, del que <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y2EeeWSfnRw\">Carlos Villuendas hizo un pr√°ctico tutorial</a>.</p>\n<p>Otras herramientas analizan peri√≥dicamente las webs que indiquemos y nos alertar√°n cuando alguna de las m√©tricas empeora sustancialmente. Recomendamos <a href=\"https://calibreapp.com\">Calibre</a>, <a href=\"https://www.debugbear.com\">DebugBear</a>, <a href=\"https://www.sitespeed.io/\">SiteSpeed</a> y <a href=\"https://speedcurve.com/\">SpeedCurve</a>.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1240px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/200b774a1d4efe55b294d08e369fb2da/f7947/speedcurve-guardian.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.517774343122106%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'182\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M0%2091v91h401V0H0v91m10-53c-2%201-1%202%201%202s2%200%201%202c-2%203-2%205-1%205l4-3c2-4%203-4%202-1%200%203%203%205%206%203%202%200%202-1%202-3v-2l1%204c0%202%204%203%206%201%203-3%201-9-3-9l-3%202h-2c-2-2-13-2-14-1m25%200c-2%201-1%209%201%209l1-2h2c3%203%205%202%203-2-1-1-2-2-1-3%202-2%203-1%203%203s0%204%203%204c4%200%205-1%205-5%200-3-1-4-2-5-4%200-10%200-11%202h-2c0-2-1-3-2-1m176%200l-1%202%202%203%203%201h-3c-3%200-2%202%202%203l3-1c0-2%203-2%206%200%202%202%205-1%203-3l-1-3c0-3-1-3-4%200l-4%202-2-1c-2-1-2-1%200-1%203%200%203-3-1-3l-3%201M64%20120c0%204%201%205%204%204%203-2%203-2%204%202%202%205%206%204%207-2%201-3%201-4%202-2%201%207%200%207%2011%207l9-1c2-4%202-10%201-10l-1%204c0%205-1%206-9%206h-8l-1-5c-2-7-4-7-5%201-1%205-3%205-5%200-1-3-6-5-6-2%200%202-2%200-2-2-1-2-1-2-1%200\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/200b774a1d4efe55b294d08e369fb2da/277cf/speedcurve-guardian.webp 310w,\n/static/200b774a1d4efe55b294d08e36